data.description:
SELLER OFFERING $10,000 TOWARDS BUYER CONCESSIONS OR TO BUY DOWN THE RATE. Welcome to Port Dixie.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has been well maintained and is move-in ready and the roof was replaced in 2019. All flooring in bedrooms.  The open concept layout connects the kitchen, dining room, and living room.  New kitchen cabinets and counter tops were added by sellers. Newer stainless steel appliances well. Updated vanity and sink in 2nd bedroom and updated vanity and sink, step in shower and beautiful shiplap in master bedroom. Access the beautifully landscaped back yard paradise that offers an outdoor shower and storage building through one of the two sliding glass doors in the living room and dining room, as well as the door in the master bedroom. Spend your weekends relaxing in the shade of mature trees surrounded by a privacy fence.

Florida living at its finest with no HOA and minutes from Eglin Air Force Base and the Destin/VPS airport. Schedule your showing appointment today!  

Seller has a survey and may possibility have a home warranty that can be transferred. Also has WDO inspection performed every year. 

Refrigerator and freezer in garage do not convey. Security cameras do not convey.
